summary: Retexture of ESO Nord Armor by Newermind43
descriptionHtml:
This is retexture of ESO Nord Armor made by Newermind43.
Orginal mod is here:
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68530/?

[s]to use unpack contents of archive to Skyrim folder, replacing Newermind43's textures.
[/s]File removed due to Original asset author request. Should be available on his mod page soon.

I found orginal textures a little too generic and clean, so I've tweaked them a bit.
author: BullGod
